Cea Amarin
Cea is a 75-year-old farmer who have very experienced with agriculture. She wants to find a way to maintain the farm by herself, as she is aged she found herself lack of physical strength after ages. She mounted our deveices to the farm and logged into our webapp to monitor the situation of the field. She monitor situation in the farm easily by seeing the numbers and charts on the website. She also connected her original watering device into the system so she can finish daily job at home on her own. She was also able to determine the situsion by the colour of light and follow suggestions given on website which are determined by our database. She was able to live a more satisfied way. 
